Product description

Below Knee Pencil Skirt

Measurements:

Small: Waist - 26", Hips - 36", Length - 27"
Medium:Waist - 28", Hips - 38", Length - 27"
Large:Waist - 30", Hips - 40", Length - 27"
Extra Large:Waist - 32", Hips - 42", Length - 27"

Join the Simlu Fashion Club

These Below the Knee Pencil Skirt for Women symbolize fashion and style. The loose fitting, flowing look has a slimming effect. The blend of Polyester, Spandex and Rayon makes for a very soft and comfortable fabric with a nice stretch that is thick enough not to ever turn see through. The knee length of the skirt makes it suitable for office and formal wear. They are trendy, pretty, and comfortable, which makes these skirts form a true fashion statement, while leaving you with the maximum comfort. These pencil skirts offer a comfortable, stylish look for women who want to look good and feel comfortable at the same time.

Simlu Womens Below the Knee Pencil Skirt

These Pencil Skirts for Women are cool skirts with a classy look. They are affordable skirts for women who love themselves. Enjoy this pencil skirt with a long cardigan, tailored top, or whatever else you are in the mood of, to achieve the look you want today! Spice up your work clothes with the many prints and colors available, including black, white, floral, and more. These skirts are a classic, and will never become old-fashioned. You are going to love and use these for years!
